1. Open a file 


	vim "file name"

2. Move in file 

	H - left
	J - down
	K - Up
	L - right

	$ nhay ve cuoi dong hien tai
	0 nhay ve dau dong hien tai
	
	gg go to top
	
	G Nhay xuong cuoi file 

	50G Nhay toi dong 50 cua file

	CRTR + G hien tho thon tin dong hien tai, tong so dong

3. High light
	
	v -- Highlight mot vong tex duoc chon bangw H/J/K/L
	V -- Chon nhanh dong hien ta


	vap - chon doan van ban hien tai

	ggVG -- Chon toan bo file

4. Tim kiem

	/n -- Tim kiem

5. Chinh sua noi dung

	i - insert
	R - Thay the
	x - xoa vi tri contro

6- Thoat and save

	:q - Thoat
	:q! bat buoc thoat khong can luu
	:w! Bat buoc ghi file de
	:wq - Luu xong thoat
	:w luu file 
